有食奇異果嘅習慣，就速速落街買左一堆每日啪兩個<br />\n屌你呢幾日完全唔痛，而家仲開始埋口，真係好撚勁<br />\n除左富含維生素，醫痱滋一流外，最重要係易揀<br />\n揀橙有時睇落好靚，屌一食酸到抽筋<br />\n相反奇異果只要掐落軟身，就算唔甜都唔會酸，十分好揀<br />\n食又方便快捷，企係鋅盤，拎起一切一挖一啪，就已經半個<br />\n食兩個全程不過兩分鐘，係忙碌都市人嘅最佳選擇<br />\n<br />\n奇異果真係好撚正，簡直就係神的恩惠哦！</blockquote><br />\n，最重要係易揀？？？<br />\n揀橙有時睇落好靚，屌一食酸到抽筋？？。<br />\n咁係你有撚病姐，Citysuper 啲華倫西亞橙正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果種鮮果種甜同橙香味係其他品種嘅橙冇得比</blockquote><br />\n又做乜撚嘢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e1a1d7574940b83fee8ea0cf06e2ecefd45342","tid":352273,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:11:11.000Z","msg":"重可以自家種添架<br />\n擺啲奇異種子落泥度<br />\n再淋返三五七日水就有奇異果食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796e74f27f2e23dd3a62dc716b7b752879e23f4d","tid":352273,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"係，有次初發，即刻去7仔買支奇異果汁"},{"pid":"b03901c4a7353dbaaa88cefa8fad25808ca18cf3","tid":352273,"uid":54390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"原來咁多人同我諗法一樣"},{"pid":"0e793fea380e6e1aca3d7b6af491d490a191e6a7","tid":352273,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:25:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以連皮食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係連皮食，講俾人聽俾人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece0f4eef41438b6abd4a7741c89f578bf713387","tid":352273,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T03:41:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以連皮食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係連皮食，講俾人聽俾人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /